Bahrain to Complete Shariah Trust Guidelines by Year End

-- B y   D o n n a   A b u   N a s r
-- 
2011-09-26T06:58:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/bahrain-to-complete-shariah-trust-guidelines-by-year-end.html
Bahrain’s central bank plans to
complete guidelines for Islamic real-estate investment trusts
and private investment plans by year end, the bank’s executive
director of financial institutions supervision said today.  The central bank is in the final stages of incorporating
the rules, which will boost undertakings for collective
investment, Abdul Rahman al-Baker said at an Islamic finance
conference in Manama, Bahrain, today  To contact the reporter on this story:
Donna Abu Nasr in Dubai at 
 dabunasr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  